String.string: Meet with Grunath at the Feral Valley Station.
Meet Kechaku at the Experior Outpost in Feral Valley.
Climb the cliff near the Arena of Blood and fight the gula executors.
Report to Paduk of the Emissary Point in the Feral Valley that the gula executors have been killed.
Find the secret cave entrance near the Arena of Blood. Go to the meeting point, then use the summoning flute.
This Graatush must be the contact.
Kill Badoask in the Arena of Blood. Take his head.
Take Badoask's head to Karba at Emissary Point.
Kill Vadrask and bring back his head.
Take Vadrask's head to Karba at Emissary Point.
Deliver Karba's letter to Lauma in Frontera.
